    {
        "url": "/quotes/bill_viola_529974",
        "quote": "When you come into my pieces, it's not an intellectual experience, it's a physical experience. It's coming at your body. There's light, there's sound, the lights in some pieces are going on and off. There's loud roaring sound happening.",
