    {
        "url": "/quotes/bill_viola_529963",
        "quote": "Emotions are the key to many aspects of life. They are precisely the elements that make human beings human. I think the fact that emotions have been reduced and put off to the side in intellectual work, particularly in the 20th Century, is tragic.",
